title: WOX
about: WOX is a AI powered Discord bot created by **simple6502** and it was **95**% written by **GPT-4**! This bot provides AI driven features to discord servers! Some of what WOX v1 offers is **Text 2 Image**, **Image 2 Text**, **Image 2 Image**, A **customizable chatbot** (**ChatGPT Intergration**), and more overall utility features! Along with that, there is more things such as **Text 2 Video** coming soon!
toBegin: To start using the bot, type '**X/help**' to see a list of available commands. To see more detail about a certain command, do '**X/help [command]**'!
